emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group of women, including Phyllis Washington, Louise Farrish, Ruth Williams seated on left wearing long light colored dress with dark striped trim, Fanetta Nelson, Pauline Bolden, Marjorie Stephens, Marie Woods, and Mazie Wells, seated at tables in Loendi Club for Wynona Graves annual dinner for LaSalle students and friends
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 23, 1939, pg. 10, reads: "Wynona Graves Fetes LaSalle Students and Friends at Dinner in Loendi - Colorful among the pre-Christmas festive events was the annual dinner given by Wynona Graves to her LaSalle students and friends in Loendi's beautiful dining room Saturday evening. The guests included many out-of-towners... Others in photo below: Phyllis Washington, Louise Farrish, Ruth Williams, Fanetta Nelson, Pauline Bolden, Marjorie Stephens, Marie Woods, Mazie Wells.  Out-of-towners, Sallie Young, Welch, W.Va.; Rosa Moore, New Jersey; Sarah Moss, New York; Velma Knappes, Canonsburg; Miss Jibbes. - Harris Photo."
